description:
Insecurity; corruption; struggle; these are probably some of the most popular terms in the Nigerian society, not just as words but as the reality. 
When a story gets too long from repetition, it can be summarised shortly. “I will make your lives easier; I will secure your lives and properties” I have grown some empathy having eaten with you my poor citizens; 
I will build all your bridges and give you 24 hours power supply; I will make food cheap; I can relate to your pain; When I become the president, I will…”In short: “Just Vote for me, I wan spoil your life finish”
